- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper uses fingerprinting and sampling techniques. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is relevant as the LCE problem is a fundamental problem in string algorithms and combinatorics. 
- cs.AL (Algorithms) is also relevant as the paper proposes new algorithms for solving the LCE problem.
